text: Nachapkino () is a rural locality (a village) in Milovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 28 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Ufa, 7 km from Milovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Nachapkino
